name: ibis-vega-transform
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ibis-vega-transform" %}
{% set version = "5.3.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/Quansight/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 92a1971682d12b26dd64e77f14c5805e1c2ed0bed0d41f2a09e10366eaad0152

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install --no-deps -vv ."

requirements:
  host:
    - jupyterlab 3.*
    - jupyter-packaging 0.7.9
    - nodejs >=12
    - pip
    - python >=3.7,<3.9
    - setuptools >=46.4.0
  run:
    - altair >=4.0.0
    - altair-transform
    - graphviz
    - ibis-framework >=1.3.0
    - jaeger
    - jaeger-client
    - jupyterlab 3.*
    - jupyter-jaeger >=1.0.4
    - jupyterlab_server
    - mypy_extensions
    - nodejs >=12
    - nbclassic =>0.2
    - notebook
    - opentracing
    - pymapd >=0.24
    - python >=3.7,<3.9
    - sqlalchemy <1.4
    - tornado
    - typing_extensions

test:
  imports:
    - ibis_vega_transform
  commands:
    - jupyter labextension list 2>&1 | grep -ie "ibis-vega-transform.*OK"

about:
  home: https://github.com/Quansight/ibis-vega-transform
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Python evaluation of Vega transforms using Ibis expressions
  dev_url: https://github.com/Quansight/ibis-vega-transform

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - scopatz
    - xmnlab
